<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<!--
ghul purity overlay for System.Console.

Stream writes mutate an external sink (stdout/stderr), not
caller-reachable state — formally impure but narrowing-pure when
called as a static. Classify as MUT: NARROWING_FLOW.on_call's
MUT-with-no-receiver branch is a no-op, so path-presence facts
in the caller's narrowing env survive the call.

JB's ExternalAnnotations doesn't cover System.Console at all
(no `tools/jetbrains-annotations/System.Console/` folder), so
no conflict with JB to manage here.
-->
